name: SCORPIO
description: Scorpio is one of the most misunderstood signs of the zodiac. Because of its incredible passion and power, Scorpio is often mistaken for a fire sign. In fact, Scorpio is a water sign that derives its strength from the psychic, emotional realm. Beginning of the week in a HODL of observation of the various markets: you are trying to discover that BTD – Buy The Dip that you so desire!
